<table width="600">
	<tr>
		<td>
			<h1 align="center">Methods for Retrieving Multimedia</h1>
			<hr>			
		
			<p><b>Concept-Based Retrieval</b></p>
			<ul>
				<li>&nbsp;Use words to retrieve multimedia objects
</li>
				<li>&nbsp;<i><b>Examples</b></i>:
Title, Subject Heading,
Keyword, Caption
</li>
				</ul>
				<p><b>Content-Based Retrieval </b></p>
				<ul>
					<li>Use visual/audio features to retrieve multimedia
</li>
					<li><i><b>Examples</b></i>:
Size,
Color,
Texture,
Trajectory </li>
					</ul>

		</td>
	</tr>
</table>
</center>

